name: Fake Pixel Ricardus
description:
FOMO DYOR Fakers cashmere jersey modeled by Fake Pixel Ricardus.

Simulated pixelation. Watercolor and color pencil on wove paper.
 
Model interpretation based on Ricardus by @3a5a1a

The knit jersey offers a modern take on a motif inspired by the DYOR house archives. Crafted in cashmere, it boasts a chartreuse metallic sheen completed by a brushed finish for added softness. Letters embroidered in fine violet silk thread. The jersey has ribbed piping at collar and sleeves and will lend a bold touch to any of the season's looks. 

$2800 USD

Do your own research.
